📊 Project Title
Student Performance Analysis 

🎯 Objective
The objective of this project is to analyze how screen time, study hours, and extracurricular activities impact student performance. The dashboard provides clear insights using Excel Pivot Tables, charts, and KPIs.

📁 Dataset Description
The dataset contains information about students with the following fields:

Student_ID

Age

Gender

Study_Hours

Test_Scores

Extra_Curricular_Hours

Screen_Time_Hours (added/assumed)

🔧 Data Preparation
The following calculated fields were created:

Screen Time Category

Low (0–2 hrs)

Medium (2–4 hrs)

High (>4 hrs)

Age Group

15 & Below

16–17

18+

Flags

High Screen Time Flag

Low Score Flag

Study Flag

